                <div class="vc_article">
                    
                                            <div class="va_con _j_master_content" data-cs-t="ginfo_kw_hotel">
    <div class="block-loading loading_backward"></div>
<div class="_j_content_box">
	        <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265005301">
            续《&nbsp;2017，碎片拾忆（之一）四季颐和》
        </p>
            <div data-seq="262489052" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">碧云寺</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262489004">
            碧云寺是京西很有名的古刹，位于香山北门。早在1957年，碧云寺就被<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>市政府列为首批重点文物保护单位。2001年6月，更是被国务院列为全国重点文物保护单位。<br />
碧云寺坐西朝东，占地四万多平方米，建筑层层递增，形成一座因山势布局的佛寺建筑。自山门至塔院，纵深六重院落，高差百余米，中轴线依次排列着山门、天王殿（又称<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/17298.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="弥勒" target="_blank">弥勒</a>殿）、大雄宝殿（又称释迦牟尼殿）、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>殿、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>纪念堂（原名普明妙觉殿）和金刚宝座塔。南轴线有禅堂院、罗汉堂、藏经阁；北轴线有行宫、水泉院。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265935266" data-seq="265935278" data-pid="265935266" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/265935266.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/EC/wKgBZ1oMUaGAdATOAA4JJZi_JUs49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/EC/wKgBZ1oMUaGAdATOAA4JJZi_JUs49.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265935266" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21933.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21933" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>碧云寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265938145">
            碧云寺创建于元至顺二年（1331年），明、清两代对寺庙进行扩建，才使寺庙有了今天的规模，仔细观察寺庙正门的砖瓦，我们也确实能看出其年代的久远。<br />
碧云寺山门悬汉、满、蒙、藏四种文字的寺匾，镌刻乾隆手书的三个大字“碧云寺”。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265935267" data-seq="265935279" data-pid="265935267" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/265935267.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/ED/wKgBZ1oMUaKAJUyfAAbNUPQiocs55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/ED/wKgBZ1oMUaKAJUyfAAbNUPQiocs55.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265935267" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21933.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21933" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>碧云寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265935287">
            <img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/240@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;看点：金刚宝座塔<br />
碧云寺最出名且一定不能错过的景点当属金刚宝座塔。金刚宝座塔仿造五塔寺内宝塔建造，在整个京城，这样的宝塔仅存三座，实属珍品。宝塔位于塔院内，塔院在整个碧云寺最深处。只不过由于现在宝塔已不对外开放，所以来这游玩的话，就只能远观了！<br />
宝塔原址曾是魏忠贤之墓，清朝年间，康熙得知碧云寺为魏忠贤衣冠冢之后，传旨平毁了魏墓和石碑。后来，乾隆又下令在被平毁的魏墓处修建了金刚宝座塔，也就是我们今日所见之塔。宝塔高约34.7米，塔上刻有乾隆帝亲手撰写的“灯在菩提”四个大字。1925年，孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>先生去世之后便停灵在此，直到四年后才移灵<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10684.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="南京" target="_blank">南京</a>，现在宝塔内依然还有孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>先生的衣冠冢。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265935272" data-seq="265935284" data-pid="265935272" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/265935272.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/F3/wKgBZ1oMUaiALV2-AA78FSdU3V849.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/7F/F3/wKgBZ1oMUaiALV2-AA78FSdU3V849.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="265935272" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/21933.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21933" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>碧云寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265936545">
            <img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/240@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;看点：孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>纪念堂<br />
​孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>纪念堂本来是普明妙觉殿，因孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>先生逝世后灵柩停于寺内的金刚宝座塔，之后才将普明妙觉殿改为孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>纪念堂。<br />
纪念堂正厅前檐横匾&nbsp;“孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>纪念堂”六个字为宋庆龄夫人手书。正厅中央安放有孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>先生的汉<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10638.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="白玉" target="_blank">白玉</a>全身坐像，背后是高大的朱红漆雕屏风。南侧陈列孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>墨宝、遗著，北侧陈放着1925年3月30日苏联政府送来的水晶钢棺。厅内左右汉<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10638.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="白玉" target="_blank">白玉</a>石墙壁上镌刻着&quot;孙<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10514.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="中山" target="_blank">中山</a>致苏联遗书&quot;全文。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265935274" data-seq="265935286" data-pid="265935274" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/265935274.html">
