            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265937142">
            <img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/240@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />&nbsp;&nbsp;看点：古树<br />
寺院内有许多参天<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/145805.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="大树" target="_blank">大树</a>，大多为国槐、白皮松、七叶树和银杏
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_265935268" data-seq="265935280" data-pid="265935268" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
