                <a href="/poi/21933.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="21933" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>碧云寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262490768">
            春暖花开之际，碧云寺的梅花会吸引大量的游客前来寻香赏花，我错过了梅花盛放，赶上了垂丝海棠摇曳生香，乐哉。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262488372" data-seq="262488385" data-pid="262488372" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
