                    <i class="house"></i>碧云寺
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="265930842">
            下图：紫丁香&nbsp;&nbsp;【木樨科&nbsp;&nbsp;丁香属】&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262488373" data-seq="262488386" data-pid="262488373" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="21933">
