            <div data-seq="262489330" data-index="2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">玲珑公园</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262491312">
            <a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>昆玉河畔西八里庄，有个玲珑公园，公园里的玲珑塔已经有400多年历史。玲珑塔原名<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16593.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="永安" target="_blank">永安</a>万寿塔，因为原属慈寿寺内建筑，又称“慈寿寺塔”。住在附近的人都知道那句<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>民谣：“玲珑塔，塔玲珑，玲珑宝塔十三层。”<br />
1957年10月，慈寿寺塔被定为<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>市第一批重点文物保护单位。现尽存塔和两通石碑。<br />
1987年被列为划定保护范围及建设控制地带，保护范围四至现状围墙。<br />
1990年海淀区政府以慈寿寺塔为中心，建成玲珑公园，免费向市民开放。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262489923" data-seq="262489937" data-pid="262489923" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="843781">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/262489923.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E2/wKgBZ1n0dw2AW1MSABEi4WymwjM92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E2/wKgBZ1n0dw2AW1MSABEi4WymwjM92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262489923" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/843781.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="843781" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>玲珑公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_262489924" data-seq="262489938" data-pid="262489924" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="843781">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/262489924.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E3/wKgBZ1n0dw-AQg-fABDMJbL8oTM79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E3/wKgBZ1n0dw-AQg-fABDMJbL8oTM79.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262489924" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/843781.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="843781" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>玲珑公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_262489929" data-seq="262489943" data-pid="262489929" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="843781">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/262489929.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E8/wKgBZ1n0dxSANArOAAs51tsTUUE80.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E8/wKgBZ1n0dxSANArOAAs51tsTUUE80.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262489929" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/843781.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="843781" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>玲珑公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262491391">
            这是一座八角密檐十三层实心砖塔，始建于明万历时期，全名为慈寿寺塔，是万历皇帝生母为巩固自己地位而建。当年，李太后虽贵为太后，因出身卑微，不能与皇帝与皇后平起平坐，遂声称自己乃九莲<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/144576.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="菩萨" target="_blank">菩萨</a>转生，广建佛寺，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>慈寿寺即为她建的最著名寺院，惜光绪年间一把火烧光，仅剩下孤傲的玲珑塔。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262489926" data-seq="262489940" data-pid="262489926" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="843781">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/262489926.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E5/wKgBZ1n0dxGAKZ_OAA3g5RWfxS450.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E5/wKgBZ1n0dxGAKZ_OAA3g5RWfxS450.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262489926" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/843781.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="843781" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>玲珑公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262491492">
            玲珑塔为八角13层密檐实心砖塔（在一个高大的塔身上有多层密檐，称为“密檐塔”），高近60米，由塔基、塔身、塔刹三部分组成，秀美端庄，古色古香。<br />
塔基分上下两层，下层为边角镶石的三层平台，上层是双层须弥座，雕有精美的莲花座台。<br />
须弥座上部雕刻有笙、箫、琴、瑟等古代乐器，有十分珍贵的史料价值。<br />
但由于长年的风化，现在已经模糊不清，很难辨认。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262489927" data-seq="262489941" data-pid="262489927" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="843781">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/262489927.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:510px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E6/wKgBZ1n0dxKAUfV-AA5krzfhpmI91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E6/wKgBZ1n0dxKAUfV-AA5krzfhpmI91.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262489927" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/843781.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="843781" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>玲珑公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="262491526">
            塔身四面有砖雕的拱券门和半圆形雕窗。<br />
拱券门上的匾额分别是：南面“<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/16593.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="永安" target="_blank">永安</a>万寿塔”，东面“镇静皇图”，北面“真慈洪范”，西面“辉腾日月”。<br />
每层有佛龛24个，原供奉铜佛312尊。<br />
门窗两侧塑有金刚力士像，这些塑像历经风雨，如今都露出了木芯。<br />
塔身各处布满砖雕和泥塑人物像，均遭到严重风化，但仍可辨出当年威武雄浑和俊美生动的风采。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_262489928" data-seq="262489942" data-pid="262489928" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="843781">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8158366/262489928.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:906px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E7/wKgBZ1n0dxOAD-FzAA3eUhu2QJ474.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/E7/wKgBZ1n0dxOAD-FzAA3eUhu2QJ474.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="262489928" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/843781.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="843781" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>玲珑公园
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
    
</div>
<div class="block-loading loading_forward"></div>

